1949
01:45:45.541 --> 01:45:48.708
You make me feel brave.

1950
01:45:53.208 --> 01:45:54.875
You make me feel everything.

1951
01:45:59.791 --> 01:46:02.041
I know that you don't need a man. Jill.

1952
